### Get all dishes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/dishes

###

### Get dish by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/dishes/1

###

### Create dish 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/dishes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pizza Carbonara",
  "description": "Pizza con mozzarella, bacon y salsa carbonara",
  "price": 12.50,
  "available": true,
  "categoryId": 1
}

